{"word":"G1211 - δή - dḗ - day - Also","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">δή</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">dḗ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">day</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Also</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>NA / Not Available</span>"},{"paragraph":"ஆகையால் - எச்சம்"},{"paragraph":"now therefore, then, verily, in truth"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Probably akin to <a href=\"#/G1161 - δέ - dé - deh/1161\">G1161</a>; a particle of emphasis or explicitness; <i>now</i>, <i>then</i>, etc.: - also, and, doubtless, now, therefore.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}